core:processNote.core:description: To return values as output from this scheduled job process we set them on the ProcessInputData of the ScheduledJob.

If topic is set then this is an All Stores broadcast in which Entity Distribution Details are not applicable and so no collation will have occurred and instead the CollationDirectory will be the File Export directory. The scheduledJobProgress.totalCount will be zero as no collation has been done and so when topic is set we skip the check for TotalCount being non-zero.
